Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:21.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}時空的迷途者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:38.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}巍峨聳立 在那尖塔之巔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:44.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}星塵似烈陽如火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:48.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}雖然耀眼 但是也看得見陰暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}迷惑內心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}漫天飄零的火星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:57.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I'm me, my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:03:00.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}生而為人何所為?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}舉世人生當何為?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:05.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}腳下之地何處是?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:02.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9}無止境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9}福地洞天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:09.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}世界從來都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:11.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}一遍遍地自我說服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:15.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}以為自己早已看清
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9}思念在流轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:18.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}雖仍有迷茫 但我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:24.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}彷徨於時空的迷途者
